name: Unfocused
description:
When you start working, but your mind wanders away. You still remember that lovely beach you went on Sunday, or that coffee you sipped while reading a book at a fancy cafe, or simply that quality time with your loved ones at home. 

Artwork for #ItsMondayArt by Monday Art Club.
GIF — 1400 x 2100 pixel

If you purchase this artwork and want to print it, feel free to ask me for high res JPEG file.
